<![CDATA[<p class="MsoNoSpacing"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">Dear {!Contact.FirstName},</font></p><p class="MsoNoSpacing"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">&nbsp;</font></p><p class="MsoNoSpacing"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">We are writing to you because you were a Team Mentor with The Challenge Network in the summer of 2012.</font></p><p class="MsoNoSpacing"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><font size="2">You will recall that the first week of your role was the Team Challenge, a particularly long week, and we have been advised that as we paid you on a weekly basis, we should have paid you more salary for that particular week.</font></span></p><p class="MsoNoSpacing"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><font size="2">This error occurred as we calculated the Team Mentor salary on the basis of the entire period worked (including both the Team Challenge week and the Real Challenge week). However, as we paid you weekly and the Team Challenge is longer, we should have allocated these funds so you were paid slightly more for the Team Challenge week and slightly less for the Real Challenge week.&nbsp;</font></span></p><p class="MsoNoSpacing"><font size="2"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">It is important to us that all Challenge Network staff are paid the right amount. &nbsp;We would therefore like to correct our error and pay you an extra Â£40 for each Team Challenge week you completed.&nbsp;</span><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">This sum is taxable and tax will be deducted in line with the tax details we hold for you.</span></font></p><p class="MsoNoSpacing"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><font size="2">From our records we believe you worked on {!Contact.00NC0000005FMpC} Team Challenge week(s) and that we would therefore like to make a payment of {!Contact.00NC0000005FStM}.</font></span></p><p class="MsoNoSpacing"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><font size="2">We also have the following bank details for you:</font></span></p><p class="MsoNoSpacing"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><font size="2">Sort code: {!Contact.Dragon_Next_Step__c}</font></span></p><p class="MsoNoSpacing"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">Account Number: {!Contact.Dragon_state_of_play__c}</font></p><p class="MsoNoSpacing"><font size="2"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">If any of the above details are incorrect, or you have any other queries, please let us know by sending an email to summerpay2012@the-challenge.org by </span><b style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">17 September 2013</b></font></p><p class="MsoNoSpacing"><b style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">If the above details are correct you need take no further action.</b></p><p class="MsoNoSpacing"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><font size="2">We will be paying all outstanding sums to you on 23 September 2013.</font></span></p><p class="MsoNoSpacing"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><font size="2">Once again we would like to apologise for the underpayment made to you last year.</font></span></p><p class="MsoNoSpacing"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><font size="2">Yours sincerely,</font></span></p><p class="MsoNoSpacing"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">&nbsp;</font></p><p class="MsoNoSpacing"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">R. Ovens</font></p><p class="MsoNoSpacing"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><font size="2">Chief Financial Officer</font></span></p><p class="MsoNoSpacing"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">The Challenge Network</font></p>]]></td>
